# 🧠 OS Concept 2: Service Discovery

🔥 Important microservices concept.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

In distributed systems:

Services constantly scale up/down.

IP addresses change dynamically.

---

## Solution

👉 Service Discovery

Services register themselves automatically.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Phone contact list updating automatically.

---

## Flow

```text id="8q2mtr"
Service starts
   ↓
Registers location
   ↓
Other services discover it
```

---

## Why Important?

✔ scalability
✔ dynamic infrastructure
✔ easier communication

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why service discovery needed?**

👉 Because service locations change dynamically in distributed systems.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="5v1xzn"
Services find each other automatically
```

