# ⚙️ COA Concept 3: Quantum Computing Basics

🔥 Future computing interview favorite.

---

## 1️⃣ Traditional Computing

Uses bits:

```text id="n2q7pk"
0 or 1
```

---

# Quantum Computing

Uses qubits.

Qubits can exist in:

```text id="6m8xra"
0 and 1 simultaneously
```

(superposition)

---

## Why Powerful?

Can solve some complex problems much faster.

---

## Key Ideas

✔ superposition
✔ entanglement
✔ quantum parallelism

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Trying many paths simultaneously in maze.

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Difference between bit and qubit?**

👉 Bits store either 0 or 1, while qubits can represent multiple states simultaneously.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="4t9qwy"
Qubit = multiple possibilities together
```

