# ⚙️ COA Concept 4: In-Memory Computing

🔥 Modern high-performance computing concept.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

Moving data between CPU and memory causes delays.

(Von Neumann bottleneck)

---

## Solution

Perform computation closer to memory or inside memory.

---

## Why Important?

✔ lower latency
✔ lower energy usage
✔ faster AI workloads

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Cooking inside grocery store instead of transporting ingredients far away.

---

## Uses

* AI acceleration
* big data analytics
* scientific computing

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why in-memory computing improves performance?**

👉 Because it reduces costly data movement between processor and memory.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="7p3mkt"
Compute near data
```

